46
00:04:07 --> 00:04:10
Let us ask LaTeX to start a new line.

47
00:04:11 --> 00:04:16
Let us write <b>alpha backslash space a</b>.

48
00:04:17 --> 00:04:19
Compile it.

49
00:04:20 --> 00:04:22
This has created a <b>space</b>.

