00:08:28 --> 00:08:32
Superscripts are created by the <b>caret</b> or the <b>up arrow</b> symbol.

92
00:08:33 --> 00:08:42
For example, if you want to create 'x' to the power 3, you will write: <b>x up arrow 3</b>.

